This is a fantastic article. The paratech is fun to envision and chunky to read without being dry, while the escalation of humanity and the Foundation's reaction to it - both inside and out - are well-paced and managed to hold my attention throughout. The ending is also extremely clever, maintaining the original theme of apotheosis while putting an ironic twist on it. My only real gripe is that it seems improbable for the Foundation to keep being able to develop increasingly advanced paratech even though their resource base has dwindled to the southwestern United States.





